OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with persistent rain,
OL,6,Fmostly in the north at first,
OL,7,Fotherwise frequent showers. These
OL,8,Fwintry over high ground with the risk
OL,9,Fof thunder at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FFrequent showers will
OL,12,Fcontinue through the evening but will
OL,13,Fclear slowly from the east overnight.
OL,14,FIt will become cold as clear spells
OL,15,Fincrease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
