OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FBright spells, a few showers
OL,6,Fwest. Cloud spreads north with rain
OL,7,Fsoon following. This heavy and
OL,8,Fpersistent with snow to low levels.
OL,9,FThe wind strengthens to severe gale
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,13,Frain, hill snow and severe gales clear
OL,14,FSunday morning, leaving a few showers.
OL,15,FMostly dry but cloudy Monday and
OL,16,FTuesday with showers then patchy rain
OL,17,Fspreading east late Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
